MOLINA
v.
S.C. (PEOPLE) S256394 Supreme Court of California. AUGUST 21, 2019 Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar, Kruger and Groban, JJ.

The petition for review is granted. The Reporter of Decisions is directed not to publish in the Official Appellate Reports the opinion in the above-entitled appeal filed May 17, 2019, which appears at 35 Cal.App.5th 531 , 247 Cal.Rptr.3d 496 . ( Cal. Const., art. VI, section 14 ; Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.1125(c)(1).)
